metadata.name: The Awakening
metadata.description:
『The Awakening』- full ver.
"Witness the transformation of the mechanized armor angel, getting into her battle-ready form."

Derivative art inspired by Killer GF.

This auction is a set collection of a full ver and a card ver:
1. I will transfer the card ver to the Bidding Winner on FND (eth).
2. Do not make an offer on the card ver.
3. The collector will get the original PNG file in 5000*5000 pixels, 300 dpi.
